snippet.title: Spitfire Audio
snippet.description: Spitfire Audio makes inspiring sounds and scoring tools in collaboration with the world's greatest composers, musicians, engineers and studios. From full orchestras to hybrid synths, each virtual instrument and sample library has been expertly sampled and developed by the Spitfire team using high-end recording techniques and cutting edge technology — designed for media composers, music creators and producers.
